======================================================================
		         Terminal DOGE
		         Version 0.0.1

                         README.install
----------------------------------------------------------------------


Overview
======================================================================
This README.install file describes how to install Terminal DOGE

It consists of the following sections:
   - Requirements
   - Installation Instructions
   - Uninstallation Instructions

Before to install the program, if you want to see Terminal DOGE execu-
ting you can access: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QxyoltnQKLU and
check a simple demonstration.

Requirements
======================================================================
To install Terminal DOGE you will need:
   - Linux with kernel 3.13 (recommended)
   - g++ version 4.8.2 (recommended)
   - cmake version 2.8.12.2 (recommended)

Installation Instructions
======================================================================

There is the required steps to install Terminal DOGE:

   1. Run theses following commands:

   # cmake .
   # make


Uninstallation Instructions
======================================================================

This section explains how to uninstall Terminal DOGE: 

   1. Uninstall Terminal DOGE with the command:

   # make clean

----------------------------------------------------------------------
======================================================================
